name: Heidi Van Horne - Framed Pinup 5x7 OVAL
description:
Available for a LIMITED TIME ONLY - ONLY ONE (1) of EACH will be offered, and they are first come, first served.  

These high quality gloss prints are some of Heidi's top images, framed in a classic black lightweight plastic frame, perfect for holiday gift giving or a lovely, ready-to-hang addition to your own home or office decor.

AVAILABLE IMAGES:
oval shaped frame with 5x7 print trimmed to fit frame

LAST ONE AVAILABLE!
- Green Dress Getaway - pinup photo by Shannon Brooke of Heidi with a 1951 Army plane and a vintage car


SOLD!-- 1930's Garbo Suite Pin Up - photo by 666 Photography of Heidi in a vintage styled gown and hair in 1930's fingerwaves, shot on location at the Garbo suite in Austin

*If your order comes right after someone else buys the item you wanted and before the store registers it as SOLD OUT, you will be offered first choice of one of the remaining images of the same size/price or a full refund.

For fast and safe shipping, all of these special offer framed prints will be shipped via USPS PRIORITY MAIL to all US buyers.  

ALL of the items listed are from Heidi's personal stock.  All offered are limited in availability.
